title: 249: Getting Enough Protein, Benefits & Detriments Of Cardio, Muscle Growth Killers & MORE
description: Sal, Adam & Justin offer up the second Quah of the week! They answer Pump Head questions about eating 1 gram of protein per pound of body weight, short-term benefits and long-term detriments of cardio, the prevalence of sick fitness people, cardio leading up to a fitness show & the biggest things that stop muscle growth dead in its tracks.
